<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1864-04-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1864-04-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="96" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d96">
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Dayton</persName></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#left">No. 533.]</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi></placeName>
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1864-04-21"><hi rend="italic">April</hi> 21, 1864.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I thank you for your interesting despatch
                            of the 4th of April, No. 446. The time which was limited for the
                            execution of the convention for removing <pb facs="0096" n="76" xml:id="pg_76"/> the French government tobacco will expire on the
                            23d. I give you a copy of a correspondence<note n="*" xml:id="d96fn1">[See correspondence with the French legation.]</note> that has
                            arisen with regard to an extension of the time.</p>
                        <p rend="center">* * * * * *</p>
                        <p>This suspension is made for that reason, and for that only.</p>
                        <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed></closer>
                        <postscript>
                            <p><hi rend="smallcaps">William L. Dayton</hi> Esq.</p>
                        </postscript>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>